quran[9{c,v,t}:
8,53,yeh is liye ke jo Nemat khuda kisi qoum ko diya karta hai jab taq woh khud apne dilon ki haalat nah badal dalain khuda usay nahi badla karta. aur is liye ke khuda santa jaanta hai
8,54,jaissa haal firounion aur un se pehlay logon ka ( howa tha waisa hi un ka howa ) unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ki ayaton ko jhatlaya to hum ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab halaak kar dala aur firounion ko duubo diya. aur woh sab zalim they
8,55,jandaroon mein sab se badter khuda ke nazdeek woh log hain jo kafir hain so woh imaan nahi laatay
8,56,jin logon se tum ne ( sulah ka ) ehadkiya hai phir woh har baar apne ehad ko toar daaltay hain aur ( khuda se ) nahi drtay
8,57,agar tum un ko larai mein pao to inhen aisi saza do ke jo log un ke pas pusht hain woh un ko dekh kar bhaag jayen ajab nahi ke un ko ( is se ) Ibrat ho
8,58,aur agar tum ko kisi qoum se dagha baazi ka khauf ho to ( un ka ehad ) inhen ki taraf pheink do ( aur ) barabar ( ka jawab do ) kuch shak nahi ke khuda daghabazon ko dost nahi rakhta
8,59,aur kafir yeh nah khayaal karen ke woh bhaag niklay hain. woh ( apni chalon se hum ko ) hargiz aajiz nahi kar saktay
8,60,aur jahan taq hosakay ( fouj ki jamiat ke ) zor se aur ghoron ke tayyar rakhnay se un ke ( muqablay ke ) liye mustaed raho ke is se khuda ke dushmanon aur tumahray dushmanon aur un ke siwa aur logon par jin ko tum nahi jantay aur khuda jaanta hai Haibat baithi rahay gi. aur tum jo kuch raah khuda mein kharch karo ge is ka sawab tum ko poora poora diya jaye ga aur tumhara zara nuqsaan nahikiya jaye ga
8,61,aur agar yeh log sulah ki taraf mael hon to tum bhi is ki taraf mael ho jao aur khuda par bharosa rakho. kuch shak nahi ke woh sab kuch santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
